{"tid":1442367,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「點解猶太人當時唔反抗呀？」 1939 vs 2019","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:40.000Z","uid":143321,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9d1392785157e160620f19c7900b98f13dfb81","tid":1442367,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"手動轉載<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2582774405106015?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F2582774405106015%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2lQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=0f72991b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2582774405106015?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n「點解猶太人當時唔反抗呀？」問這種問題者，望望身邊的香港人，自會得到解答。<br />\n猶太人由接受戴臂章去到「最終解決方案」，只是用了區區五年。納粹先將他們形容為老鼠，然後開始街道隔離，一步步收窄他們的生存空間，最後遷徙他們到集中營，整個過程，用意是蠶食人的意志，培養一種對法治的高度服從。被壓迫者也會不斷自欺說：「只要我肯服從，我就會無事。」結果邁向萬劫不復之地。<br />\n大陸人逐漸視香港人為國家問題的根源，如同當年歐洲人看待猶太人一樣。他們會漸漸覺得鎮壓這些人、槍殺這些人、囚禁這些人去集中營也是無可厚非，甚至是義舉，變成邪惡的一分子而不自知。今日13億人，皆覺得新疆興建集中營是合理的事，全因中共成功將維族人渲染成恐怖分子，把集中營包裝成社會問題的「最終解決方案」。<br />\n香港人，現在正被污名化，被形容是曱甴，我們距離「最終解決方案」還有多遠？<br />\n「唔好搞咁多嘢啦！」及「猶太人做咩唔反抗？」，通常都是出自同一人之口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KX5djaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKX5djaY.jpg&h=a385d1c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dc7nWXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDc7nWXG.jpg&h=6d9badbc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rj1Tja3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frj1Tja3.jpg&h=ab67fe45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0k1s4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0k1s4w.jpg&h=dfe923e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm2fxwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm2fxwi.jpg&h=0bfa0f11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDMggXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDMggXZ.jpg&h=c980886d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAgoGpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAgoGpH.jpg&h=e4a67405&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jShZZbr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjShZZbr.jpg&h=398d0ccd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sS8ivh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsS8ivh8.jpg&h=04880f15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a6fd3037c3bba0f40a8aee6bc8a4a25d0de8efd","tid":1442367,"uid":265499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09dce21ba6556999cbbb45b59e12d35fb729940e","tid":1442367,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"心酸"},{"pid":"06589226687fbbee6f4165ce8342cae884cf4ca0","tid":1442367,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cdd2da8d362ee068a20bdbf5eed1fc3ee9d71ce8","tid":1442367,"uid":66970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"#721"},{"pid":"e120be397771ef81c9436854793dc0e37248bf63","tid":1442367,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9d29ae398d794a14fcb8843e84da98edf3c6977","tid":1442367,"uid":172839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}